snippet.title: One Step From Eden - Steam Demo Trailer 2019
snippet.description:
One Step From Eden is a fresh new deckbuilding roguelike!
Steam Page: https://store.steampowered.com/app/960690/
Play the demo: https://www.onestepfromeden.com

One Step From Eden is a deckbuilding, action-packed, roguelike inspired by MegaMan Battle Network! The game features fast paced bullet-hell action and strategic deckbuilding.

https://twitter.com/OneStepFromEden
